# <type>(optional-scope): <short summary>
#
# Examples:
# feat(core): add record parser scaffold
# fix(nist): guard null transaction payload
# docs: describe package responsibilities
# chore(repo): align analyzer settings
#
# Allowed types:
# build, chore, ci, docs, feat, fix, perf, refactor, revert, style, test
#
# Body (optional):
# Explain why the change exists and any important context.
#
# Breaking changes:
# Add ! after the type/scope, for example:
# feat(core)!: rename public record model
